        "story_heading": "<p>Every blouse tells<br><em>a story.</em></p>",
        "story_body": "<p>Founded with a deep love for Indian craftsmanship, Vamas was born from a simple belief — every woman deserves a blouse that tells her story. We work directly with skilled karigars across India to bring you heirloom-quality pieces at honest prices.</p><p>Our name, Vamas, is rooted in the Sanskrit tradition — it means \"beautiful\" and \"belonging to the left side,\" a sacred direction in Indian culture. Each stitch we make is a tribute to the artisans whose hands carry centuries of knowledge.</p><p>From the looms of Varanasi to the block-print studios of Jaipur, every Vamas blouse is a journey across India's rich textile heritage.</p>",
